custom white balance, so make

00:00:38.420 --> 00:00:39.470
sure that you're in your

00:00:39.580 --> 00:00:40.520
manual and checking that out

00:00:40.740 --> 00:00:41.610
so you know how to do for

00:00:41.730 --> 00:00:43.340
your camera body, step number

00:00:43.550 --> 00:00:44.660
two is you're going

00:00:44.880 --> 00:00:46.080
to stand where your subject

